oblems to access help because they\'re treated like criminals.\r\n\r\nThis is because our governments refuse to take control of drugs.\r\n\r\nParents need greater tools and strategies to help their kids cope with the challenges of modern life.\r\n\r\nIt’s not good enough to put our heads in the sand and tell our kids to “just say no”. It doesn\'t work.\r\n\r\nIt\'s time to end the fear tactics. It\'s time to end the marketing gimmicks. People need real resources to reduce the harms associated with drug use.\r\n\r\nOur state and federal governments need to work together to get drug use under control by putting health and safety first.'),(6682,19,'_intro_bullets','field_5df5c6799d05a'),(6683,19,'intro_text',''),(6684,19,'_intro_text','field_5df5c6799d0c6'),(6685,19,'plan_title',''),(6686,19,'_plan_title','field_5df5c6799d197'),(6687,19,'plan_icons_row','5'),(6688,19,'_plan_icons_row','field_5df5c6799d211'),(6689,611,'banner_head','About'),(6690,611,'_banner_head','field_5b568121a8ffe'),(6691,611,'banner_sub','Sub Head'),(6692,611,'_banner_sub','field_5b568139fd366'),(6693,611,'first_image_title','The Lifestart difference'),(6694,611,'_first_image_title','field_5b67ca606afc4'),(6695,611,'first_image_cont','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet. \r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet.'),(6696,611,'_first_image_cont','field_5b67caff6afc5'),(6697,611,'first_image_button',''),(6698,611,'_first_image_button','field_5b67cb0d6afc6'),(6699,611,'second_image_title','Our Philosophy'),(6700,611,'_second_image_title','field_5b67cb20ddf9a'),(6701,611,'second_image_cont','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet. \r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet.'),(6702,611,'_second_image_cont','field_5