s known to cause respiratory infections. This new coronavirus is called COVID-19.\r\n\r\nSymptoms range from fever, tiredness, dry cough, aches and pains, nasal congestion, runny nose, sore throat or diarrhoea. Some people recover quickly and easily, and other may get very sick, very quickly.\r\n\r\n[/expand]','Conference Awards','','inherit','closed','closed','','669-revision-v1','','','2020-04-09 01:20:46','2020-04-09 01:20:46','',669,'http://localhost/669-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(671,1,'2020-04-09 01:21:19','2020-04-09 01:21:19',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','671','','','2020-04-09 01:27:00','2020-04-09 01:27:00','',0,'http://localhost/?p=671',7,'nav_menu_item','',0),(672,1,'2020-04-09 01:21:56','2020-04-09 01:21:56','<h3><strong>What is Society Fellowship?</strong></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\nSociety Fellows have been judged by their peers to have made a substantial contribution to the Australian research, insights and analytics industry.\r\n\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\nOur Fellows continue to assist the Society and the industry in Australia through their commitment of time and energy to raising awareness of the value of research within the broad community, and through volunteering their time to various projects which draw on their substantial experience and expertise.\r\n\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\nThere are currently 72 Fellows within the Society. The award of Fellowship recognises the contribution the nominee has made to the industry across the following important areas:\r\n\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>sharing practical expertise across the industry;</li>\r\n 	<li>providing ethical leadership;</li>\r\n 	<li>contributing to market research theory, original</li>\r\n 	<li>thought, conceptual structures in marketing, policy</li>\r\n 	<li>formulation or research into these areas;</li>\r\n 	<li>increasing the Australian public’s awareness of, and</li>\r\n 	<li>understanding of the value of, research, insights and</li>\r\n 	<li>analytics; and</li>\r\n 	<li>increasing the size and scale of the industry as a</li>\r\n 	<li>whole in a way that benefits the profession.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n<h3>The Fellowship Award process</h3>\r\n[expand title=\"How to nominate\" elwraptag=\"div\" elwrapclass=\"fellow-item\" tag=\"h4\"]\r\n\r\nCoronaviruses are a large family of viruses known to cause respiratory infections. This new coronavirus is called COVID-19.\r\n\r\nSymptoms range from fever, tiredness, dry cough, aches and pains, nasal congestion, runny nose, sore throat or diarrhoea. Some people recover quickly and easily, and other may get very sick, very quickly.\r\n\r\n[/expand]\r\n\r\n[expand title=\"Election of fellows criteria\" elwraptag=\"div\" elwrapclass=\"fellow-item\" tag=\"h4\"]\r\n\r\nCoronaviruses are a large family of viruses known to cause respiratory infections. This new coronavirus is called COVID-19.\r\n\r\nSymptoms range from fever, tiredness, dry cough, aches and pains, nasal congestion, runny nose, sore throat or diarrhoea. Some people recover quickly and easily, and other may get very sick, very quickly.\r\n\r\n[/expand]\r\n\r\n[expand title=\"Nomination process\" elwraptag=\"div\" elwrapclass=\"fellow-item\" tag=\"h4\"]\r\n\r\nCoronaviruses are a large family of viruses known to cause respiratory infections. This new coronavirus is called COVID-19.\r\n\r\nSymptoms range from fever, tiredness, dry cough, aches and pains, nasal congestion, runny nose, sore throat or diarrhoea. Some people recover quickly and easily, and other may get very sick, very quickly.\r\n\r\n[/expand]\r\n\r\n[expand title=\"Election process\" elwraptag=\"div\" elwrapclass=\"fellow-item\" tag=\"h4\"]\r\n\r\nCoronaviruses are a large family of viruses known to cause respiratory infections. This new coronavirus is called COVID-19.\r\n\r\nSymptoms ra